Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:53.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji, Luffy \Nand the others set out for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:57.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the Whole Cake Island where \NEmperor Big Mom waits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get caught by Big Mom!\NShe's the emperor of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, people in different countries\Nstarted preparing for the Reverie,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the World Conference\Nthat takes place every four years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NI'll do it so watch the sea, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of you must pay me 5,000 berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our allowance will be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a large headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The island, for decades \Nveiled in mystery..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...was finally revealed."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Revolutionary Army's\Ngeneral headquarters - Baltigo..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:10.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY'S HQ FOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...has already been laid to waste?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Kaido Returns!\NAn Imminent Threat to the Worst Generation!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!\NEverything is nice and fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how exactly do you cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares!\NLet's just chop everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekoms, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NI'm fatally injured but it's nothing. Grr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy does nothing but crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the worst.\NI've never seen anybody jump off Zou. Grr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, I think he's in the kitchen.\NIs anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get him. It's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY'S HQ FOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revolutionary Army got defeated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you-{\i1}gara{\i0} were\Nthe son of the revolutionary - Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo-{\i1}san{\i0}?! The other brother that \Nyou said you met at Dressrosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the Chief of Staff?!\NThat makes him No.2 of the Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unusual group of \Nthree brothers you guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Dragon guy beside him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's him!\NYour grandpa told you two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Luffy...\NI heard that you saw your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! My dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by my dad?\NI have a dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Then he didn't tell you who he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he saw you off at Rogue Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's old man was in that town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's my dad like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious... about Luffy's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Dragon.\NHe's a revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Revolutionary Army - Dragon.\NThat's your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is this my dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--After all these years?!\N--I've never seen him before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Luffy's father is\Nthe boss of the Revolutionary Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Oh my! Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you look into it at all\Nover the last couple of years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally people would care\Nif their father is such a famous figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he took care of Robin for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! I've never seen him before!\NHe doesn't really look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm worried about Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't really \Nempathize with a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The location of their general headquarters was found\Nby an anonymous tip."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"However, when the Navy and \NCipher Pol arrived there,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"the Blackbeard Pirates had already\Ndestroyed the headquarters."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard?! Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did Emperor Blackbeard want to\Nattack the Revolutionary Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in Dressrosa, Sabo fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...against the champion. Is that why?\N--Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor Blackbeard fled\Nafter butting heads with Cipher Pol, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no report on casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your-{\i1}gara{\i0} father or brother \Nhad been caught or killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that would've made headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess they're okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for cooking for us\Nbut is that normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why is it on fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I left the stove on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There's an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! Electro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furl the sail now! The \Nwind is gonna rip it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be heavy rain! It'll put it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So lucky!\N--Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's putting out the fire! Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Pour more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a hand! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook! Get cola ready to fill \Nup at a moment's notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do something, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fatally injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:58.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,ZOU
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Carrot is out at sea now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me sooner, Bariete?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry-{\i1}saru{\i0}, Wanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Carrot that she had to tell everyone\Nthat she was going-{\i1}saru{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! If I tell anybody, \Nthey'll try to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it to yourself just for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I can't keep it to myself-{\i1}saru{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't-{\i1}saru{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! She bribed you-{\i1}teia{\i0}, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No! Wh-Wh-What are \Nyou talking about-{\i1}saru{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These bananas are...\NI-I mean, they sure look delicious but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said anything about bananas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught me-{\i1}saru{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Carrot didn't wanna \Ngo behind your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.\NI'm glad to know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just worried that she was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's with Luffy and the others,\Nshe'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duke-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please get some rest.\NI'll post extra guards if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy was probably using a Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the card was lost\Nalong with the fleet that Zunesha sank...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they'll return?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better be on the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pull me up already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:56.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A CERTAIN COUNTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.14,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to confirm!\NWe were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we thought,\NJack-{\i1}sama{\i0} failed to rescue Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the man-made Devil Fruit \NSMILE trade is practically at an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a weepy drunk today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can't have more Gifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker! Oh, Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you got beaten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we'd form the strongest pirate group\Nmade of all Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:18:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been taken down by... those upstart brats\Nbefore we fulfilled that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Joker! Even though it's primarily \Nyour own fault for being weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's talking about Straw Hat these days.\NIf you underestimate him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I underestimate him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He became a quarrelsome drunk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaido-{\i1}sama{\i0}... Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy! Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!\NThey're from {\i1}the{\i0} generation, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats think they're something\Njust because they brought down a Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must realize they messed up my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!\NTell those idiots from your generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You'd better run! What we were doing \Nwas just playing at being pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass "Captain" Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We covered up the roof!\N--Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The storm passed!\NAnd we covered up the roof that was blown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved the food I made so eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We get to eat! We're hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you like it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My original curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, we can't eat uncooked rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that bitter purplish thing?\N--It's full of fish bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So much jam!\N--Something's slimy and light blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you guys be so rude\Nafter I've taken the trouble to cook this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See?!\N--How can I eat this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't knock it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you waste food!\NSanji-{\i1}san{\i0} would be mad if he heard about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had tons of food and it's all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I messed up several times\Nso I used it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That was a week's \Nworth of food for all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, Luffy's group faces a lack of provisions\Non the very first day of their voyage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy's hungry group launches a \Nhigh-stakes mission to acquire food!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They head for a Navy frontline base \Nwhere many tough soldiers are stationed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:35.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Young officers who are \Nresponsible for the Navy's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:39.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,next generation and the Straw Hats \Nget caught in a fierce battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Hungry Front! Luffy and the Navy Rookies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:50.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
